"Service Discovery, XEP-0320: Use of DTLS-SRTP in Jingle Sessions, XEP-0353: "
"Jingle Message Initiation) (@melvo)"
msgstr ""
"დაემატა აუდიო/ვიდეო ზარების მხარდაჭერა (XEP-0166: Jingle, XEP-0167: Jingle "
"RTP Sessions, XEP-0176: Jingle ICE-UDP Transport Method, XEP-0215: External "
"Service Discovery, XEP-0320: Use of DTLS-SRTP in Jingle Sessions, XEP-0353: "
"Jingle Message Initiation) (@melvo)"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
